|  hash predicates: t1.c = t2.`month`
|  row-size=28B cardinality=1.52K
|
|--04:EXCHANGE [BROADCAST]
|  |
|  02:SCAN HDFS [functional_parquet.alltypestiny t2]
|     HDFS partitions=4/4 files=4 size=11.92KB
